{"tid":141642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死10隻]雲南長途巴公路撞田螺車　釀10死38傷","createTime":"2017-03-03T05:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T07:31:34.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"451c778c4b83f8eb8d49469fc614a1787df4faf8","tid":141642,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:40:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170303/bkncn-20170303085444142-0303_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170303%2Fbkncn-20170303085444142-0303_05011_001.html&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTro9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=82270d76\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170303/bkncn-20170303085444142-0303_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n雲南臨滄市發生奪命車禍，昨晚11時33分，一輛載有兩人的重型泥罐車（俗稱田螺車），在行經祥臨公路馬鞍山隧道附近時，與一輛載有47人的長途巴相撞，導致長途巴在路上翻側，而泥罐車則翻落路下。意外目前已造成10人死亡、38人受傷。事後傷者已送院救治，警方正在調查車禍原因。<br />\n<br />\n雙位數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd822069b584814d7c587b597b2367f70a6bdec","tid":141642,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5333fa272602ad718c044f7ed4de9fcb48e84e4","tid":141642,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死就返大陸死啦，係香港撞車浪費香港醫療資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n盲炳來㗎？<br />\n人地係大陸出事，關香港鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bb550f3b88432b0d028b1c1f6bba39fd3b9a86","tid":141642,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>死就返大陸死啦，係香港撞車浪費香港醫療資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/n